              citations: [
                "Sterne, J. A. C., Savovi\u0107, J., Page, M. J., Elbers, R. G., Blencowe, N. S., Boutron, I., Cates, C. J., Cheng, H.-Y., Corbett, M. S., Eldridge, S. M., Emberson, J. R., Hern\xE1n, M. A., Hopewell, S., Hr\xF3bjartsson, A., Junqueira, D. R., J\xFCni, P., Kirkham, J. J., Lasserson, T., Li, T., McAleenan, A., \u2026 Higgins, J. P. T. (2019). RoB 2: A revised tool for assessing risk of bias in randomised trials. <em>BMJ, 366</em>, l4898."
              ]
