        //   I²   = (Q−df)/Q = 266/364 ≈ 73.1%
        //
        // τ²_PM: iterative solution of Q(τ*)=k−1=2
        //   Update: τ²_new = τ² + (Q(τ²)−2)/W(τ²)  [start τ²=0, converge ~1e−10]
        //   Converges to τ² ≈ 1.648, RE ≈ 1.167
